# Dependencies

## Core Stack

| Package | Purpose | Min Version |
|---------|---------|-------------|
| fastapi | Web framework | 0.128.0 |
| openai | AI API client | 2.16.0 |
| chromadb | Vector database | 1.4.1 |
| pydantic | Data validation | 2.10.0 |
| pdfplumber | PDF extraction | 0.11.4 |
| pillow | Image processing | 11.0.0 |

## Adding Dependencies

```bash
# Use >= for flexibility
pip install "package>=version"

# Pin exact versions only for production
pip freeze > requirements.lock
```

## Async Requirements

Always use async-compatible libraries:
- `httpx` instead of `requests`
- `aiofiles` for file I/O
- `AsyncOpenAI` client
